Interface IMobile

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Chesskull, Fireball, Korn, Lorann, Mobile, Monster, Monster_1, YellowMen

    public interface IMobile
    The IMobile interface An interface for mobile elements, including : movement functions, position-getters, and a function to kill the mobile element, removing it from the program.
    Author:
    Florent , Axel , Luc , Romain
